title: Some Amusing Annie Gameplay Footage

embed.description: Hey guys, my name is Kid W25, and today I've got some more League of Legends for you. In this video, I play with Turnip_Sniffa (Amumu) and LeesinToMe (Irelia). As always, there was a lot of laughter to be had, and I was lucky that the Yasuo that I faced against was not a good one, because that could have been messy.

body: Just another fun League video. If you guys aren't too busy, please take a look and leave me your thoughts. Thanks again.
